   NDEP Home : Get Diabetes Information

   Get Diabetes Information

     Information on Diabetes Control
     Learn all about diabetes--the types, treatments, monitoring,
     complications, and control. Link to publications on diabetes.

     Medicare Coverage of Diabetes
     Choose from a list of materials that explain Medicare's expanded
     coverage for diabetes care. NDEP, in cooperation with the Health Care
     Financing Administration (HCFA), developed these publications.

     Health Care Provider Reference Tools
     Your ready reference library. Includes diabetes management tools and
     the guiding principles of diabetes care.

     Spanish-Language Materials
     Includes materials for people with diabetes, reference materials for
     health care providers, and a media relations kit for conducting
     outreach to Hispanic/Latino communities.

     Asian-Language Materials
     Includes media relations kit for conducting diabetes outreach to
     Asian American communities.



